# Menu Snippet

## What is it?

This snippet generates a main menu for your site.

## Installation 

Put the menu.php file in your site/snippets folder

## How to use it?

    <?php snippet('menu') ?>
	    
## Customization

Customize the html in site/snippets/menu.php to get the best result for your project

